<br>
What exactly does Guard do?<br>
                          Protect?<br>
                          Intercept?<br>
<br>
I can see the skills kick in, but that doesnt tell me how they work.<br>
Also,<br>
Does the skill 'shield' actually do anything. I cant see any difference at skill 15.<br>
Also is the skill 'parry' overrated? It sems to me that it is a lot easier to block<br>
with a shield than with a sword. BUT apparently paladins w 2handed weapons<br>
can both double attack, protect 3, chant, and parry all at the same time.<br>
and better than they can with a shield.<br>
<br>
